y</caption>\n\t\n\t<tbody>\n\t<tr>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\">← <a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_136\" title=\"Chapter 136\">Previous</a></td>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_138\" title=\"Chapter 138\">Next</a> →</td>\n\t\n\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n</section>\n</aside>\n\n</p><p><b>Chapter 137</b> is titled \"Avalanche\".\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Cover_Page\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Cover Page</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Short_Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Short Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Long_Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Long Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quick_Reference\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quick Reference</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Chapter_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chapter Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Characters\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Characters</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Author_Comment\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Author Comment</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Site_Navigation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Site Navigation</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Cover_Page\">Cover Page</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_137%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Cover_Page#Color_Covers\" title=\"Cover Page\">Color Cover</a>: <a href=\"/wiki/Straw_Hat_Pirates\" title=\"Straw Hat Pirates\">Straw Hats</a> indoors: <a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a> finds his baseball retrieved by a strange bird, <a href=\"/wiki/Sanji\" title=\"Sanji\">Sanji</a> is getting ready for a date, and <a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a> is playing chess with <a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Zoro</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Short_Summary\">Short Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_137%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Sanji\" title=\"Sanji\">Sanji</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a> try to evade the avalanche created by the <a href=\"/wiki/Animal_Species/Arabasta_Saga#Lapahn\" title=\"Animal Species/Arabasta Saga\">lapahn</a>. While they attempt to flee to a high point, they continue to be chased by the ferocious animals. In order to save <a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a>, Sanji sacrifices himself and throws Luffy and Nami to a safe place and is hit by the full front of the avalanche.\n</p><p>The avalanche also heads towards <a href=\"/wiki/Drum_Island\" title=\"Drum Island\">Drum</a>'s villages. Wapol quickly escapes with the help of his <a href=\"/wiki/Devil_Fruit\" title=\"Devil Fruit\">Devil Fruit</a> powers. Convinced that it was a deliberated plan of the Straw Hats to attack him, he departs for the castle with his two lieutenants.\n</p><p>In the mountain, Luffy is safe and has found Sanji. However the cook is now unconscious.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Long_Summary\">Long Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_137%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D3&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Nefertari_Vivi\" title=\"Nefertari Vivi\">Vivi</a> and the villagers are fleeing from the avalanche.\n</p><p>Elsewhere, Luffy and Sanji try to find higher ground but are unable to escape the avalanche. Luffy grabs a tree and rides it like a sled as he grabs Sanji. They are confronted by more lapahns who throw trees at them, but Sanji kicks Luffy away while he takes the brunt of the attack and saves his friends. Luffy tries to grab Sanji's hand but only grabs his glove.\n</p><p>Meanwhile, the villagers are freaking out about the avalanche, as well as Wapol who flees on his pet.\n</p><p>Luffy dives into the snow to retrieve Sanji. After the avalanche has hit and the village is covered, Wapol eats his way out and blames the avalanche on the Straw Hats as an elaborate plot to attack him.\n</p><p>Luffy finds Sanji and begins to bring him back up the mountain. As he passes by a buried lapahn, he also pulls out the parent lapahn. The baby and adult lapahn are shocked that a human has helped them. Luffy is soon found by Wapol's men.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quick_Reference\">Quick Reference</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_137%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D4&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chapter_Notes\">Chapter Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_137%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D5&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Bighorn\" title=\"Bighorn\">Bighorn</a> is covered by an avalanche.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Animal_Species/Arabasta_Saga#Lapahn\" title=\"Animal Species/Arabasta Saga\">Lapahns</a> are shown kindness by a human, Luffy.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Sanji\" title=\"Sanji\">Sanji</a> passes out, forcing <a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a> to carry both him and <a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a>.</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters\">Characters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_137%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D6&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table class=\"CharTable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/Pirate\" title=\"Pirate\">Pirates</a>\n</th>\n<th>Citizens\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Straw_Hat_Pirates\" title=\"Straw Hat Pirates\">Straw Hat Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Monkey D. Luffy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Roronoa Zoro</a> (cover)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Sanji\" title=\"Sanji\">Sanji</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Bliking_Pirates\" title=\"Bliking Pirates\">Bliking Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Wapol\" title=\"Wapol\">Wapol</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Chess\" title=\"Chess\">Chess</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Kuromarimo\" title=\"Kuromarimo\">Kuromarimo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Robson\" title=\"Robson\">Robson</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Arabasta\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Arabasta\">Arabasta</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Nefertari_Vivi\" title=\"Nefertari Vivi\">Nefertari Vivi</a></li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Author_Comment\">Author Comment</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_137%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D7&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><br />\n</p><table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin: auto; text-align: center; width:50%\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">Author Comment</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:90%\"><div class=\"tabber wds-tabber\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__wrapper with-bottom-border\"><ul class=\"wds-tabs\"><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab wds-is-current\" data-hash=\"Translation\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Translation</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Original\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Original</a></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\"><p><br />\nI got hit pretty hard. Here I was thinking I was invincible when I had my first fever in 10 years. Now I know first-hand how bad Nami felt. Luffy! Hurry up and get her to a doctor!!</p></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content\"><p><br />\nヒドイ目にあった。無敵の筈の僕が10年ぶりに発熱。ナミの辛さを知る。ルフィ!!ナミを早く医者に連れてってあげなさい!!</p></div></div>—<a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\">Eiichiro Oda</a></td><td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\"><img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/a/ad/Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20230801133230\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Eiichiro Oda WSJ Avatar.png\" data-image-key=\"Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"><i>English translation by <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.thegrandline.com/odatocLIVE.htm\">Greg Werner</a>. For comprehensive translation credits, see <a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments#Translation_Credits\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">here</a>.</i></td></tr>\n\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Site_Navigation\">Site Navigation</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_137%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D8&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"toccolours\" style=\"margin:auto; text-align:center; width:80%;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left;\">\n<p><b>← <a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_136\" title=\"Chapter 136\">Previous Chapter</a></b>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\">\n<p><b><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_138\" title=\"Chapter 138\">Next Chapter</a> →</b>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody>